div.p:
“Presently two countrymen passed by; but, pausing near the cottage, they entered into conversation, using violent 

gesticulations; 
               but I did not understand what they said, as they spoke the language of the country, which differed from that of my protectors. Soon after, however, Felix approached with another man: I was surprised, as I knew that he had not quitted the cottage that morning, and waited anxiously to discover, from his discourse, the meaning of these unusual appearances.
